00:59:55.640 --> 00:59:58.820
product occurs under the influence of a

00:59:58.820 --> 01:00:03.320
change in its own price, then they say

01:00:03.320 --> 01:00:09.100
about a change in the amount of demand.

01:00:09.180 --> 01:00:11.740
In this case, the demand curve does not

01:00:11.740 --> 01:00:14.880
shift, but we are going as if on the

01:00:14.880 --> 01:00:16.840
demand curve.

