01:05:30.340 --> 01:05:33.900
under natural conditions.

01:05:34.800 --> 01:05:35.520
No more can.

01:05:35.620 --> 01:05:38.520
For the sake of simplicity, we introduce this.

01:05:38.620 --> 01:05:40.360
This is the simplification.

01:05:41.460 --> 01:05:45.300
But, obviously, every producer

01:05:45.300 --> 01:05:48.220
would like to sell their oil

