01:51:25.450 --> 01:51:26.810
limited resources of any

01:51:26.810 --> 01:51:29.310
kind, material, labor,

01:51:29.410 --> 01:51:31.530
natural, finished products.

01:51:32.290 --> 01:51:33.210
So what is the idea?

01:51:33.210 --> 01:51:37.610
To produce something, we need resources.

01:51:38.250 --> 01:51:39.670
And the production function shows

01:51:39.670 --> 01:51:42.350
the relationship between what?

01:51:42.890 --> 01:51:44.970
Between the amount of

01:51:44.970 --> 01:51:48.310
resources used and

01:51:48.310 --> 01:51:50.510
the maximum output

01:51:50.650 --> 01:51:51.930
output volume that can

01:51:51.930 --> 01:51:55.370
be achieved provided

01:51:55.370 --> 01:51:58.470
that all available resources

01:51:58.470 --> 01:52:02.070
are used fully

01:52:02.070 --> 01:52:03.770
and most efficiently.

01:52:03.770 --> 01:52:05.990


