01:52:14.930 --> 01:52:16.850
bake, if she works normally,

01:52:16.850 --> 01:52:18.850
not unworking, but better

01:52:18.850 --> 01:52:21.850
organized her work, she can

01:52:21.850 --> 01:52:24.690
afford to bake 10 cakes.

01:52:25.410 --> 01:52:29.050
So if we indicate the quantity of

01:52:29.050 --> 01:52:31.590
