VC is variable cost, variable

02:27:17.910 --> 02:27:18.930
cost.

02:27:19.710 --> 02:27:21.730
The total cost is TC.

02:27:22.190 --> 02:27:25.470
Total costs of the company.

02:27:28.030 --> 02:27:31.710
It is also important to know

02:27:31.710 --> 02:27:36.850
the unit cost or average cost.

02:27:37.050 --> 02:27:40.510
The average constant cost is indicated

02:27:40.510 --> 02:27:42.490
by the letter AFC.

02:27:43.230 --> 02:27:44.470
Look at the slide.

02:27:44.710 --> 02:27:46.790
These are fixed costs

02:27:46.890 --> 02:27:48.910
per unit of production.

02:27:49.270 --> 02:27:53.730
AFC is equal to FC constant

02:27:53.730 --> 02:27:55.690
cost divided

02:27:55.690 --> 02:27:57.250
by Q.

