What are the average constant costs?

02:35:55.420 --> 02:35:56.840
We have already talked about it.

02:35:58.020 --> 02:36:01.120
They are obtained by dividing the constant cost

02:36:01.120 --> 02:36:03.520
by the volume of production.

02:36:05.890 --> 02:36:07.790
The constant cost number does not change,

02:36:07.790 --> 02:36:10.850
and the volume of production denominator

02:36:10.850 --> 02:36:11.970
changes.

