02:39:03.680 --> 02:39:06.040
Accordingly, the cost of purchasing beer grows

02:39:06.040 --> 02:39:09.220
with the volume of sales, that is, it grows

02:39:09.220 --> 02:39:10.960
with the volume of production.

02:39:11.460 --> 02:39:13.800
Therefore, for trade, the purchase

02:39:13.800 --> 02:39:16.800
